32:32.015 --> 32:44.333
Isaiah said it this way, surely he has borne our griefs and carried our sorrows, yet we esteemed him stricken smitten by God and afflicted, but he was pierced for our transgressions.

32:45.114 --> 32:53.266
He was crushed for our iniquities upon him was the chastisement that brought us peace and with his wounds we are healed.

32:55.426 --> 33:05.556
