Didn't belong to either one of us, a guy that owned the dog, asked us to take his dog out hunting.

37:57.201 --> 38:03.474
And we were hunting down at the beach, and where at the beach, the dog apparently got thirsty, ran down, and he started drinking salt water.

38:04.610 --> 38:07.714
We kept trying to get the dog to come back and make him stop.

38:08.315 --> 38:09.156
And you know how it goes?

38:09.196 --> 38:13.663
The more salt water the dog drank, the thirst of the dog got sick of running back to get more salt water.

38:14.304 --> 38:19.231
