38:21.153 --> 38:22.916
Finally, my dad came to pick us up.

38:23.937 --> 38:30.066
The dog jumped into his car, hung his head over the back seat, and promptly threw up all the salt water in my dad's car.

38:32.578 --> 38:34.861
Now my question is, what is your salt water?

38:36.303 --> 38:37.325
What is that thing?

38:37.385 --> 38:44.915
What is your massage and Maribah, the thing that you get wound up and anxious and argumentative about and just feel you have to have?

38:47.358 --> 38:52.766
Maybe like the woman at the well is romance, the next new relationship.

38:54.749 --> 39:01.458
