If you need some help just to

44:16.418 --> 44:21.744
process and meditate your way through Jesus' Sermon on the Mount, this might help you out with that.

44:24.347 --> 44:26.870
You see, ultimately we are what we drink.

44:28.072 --> 44:29.974
What do we feed our souls on?

