The challenge that Paul lays before us is that we drink from the rock, that we meditate on Jesus, we find our soul satisfaction in him,

44:46.434 --> 44:56.087
Here's what the Apostle John said as part of his great revelation, the last book of the Bible, Revelation 22, 17, the spirit and the bride say, come.

44:57.388 --> 45:01.574
Let the one who hears say, come and let the one who is thirsty, come.

45:02.415 --> 45:06.841
Let the one who desires take the water of life without price.

